Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:01.850
That's right, whenever
this app is running,

00:00:01.850 --> 00:00:04.860
it's keeping the cell radio
powered on continuously.

00:00:04.860 --> 00:00:08.140
In fact, the radio updates alone,
are enough to prevent

00:00:08.140 --> 00:00:10.940
the radio from ever returning to idle.

